title: Holding Me Still
lyrics:
The name that has brought revelation
Echoing all through the ages
Speaking to me, still speaking to me
The name with no end or beginning
Steady when my world is spinning
Right here with me, still right here with me



So when I call upon You, it's not in vain

Everything changes



Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, holding me still

Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, holding me still



The name that is over creation

Set boundaries around the ocean

Is keeping me now, still keeping me now

The name with the power like thunder

Moving through signs and wonders

Inside of me now, inside of me now



So when I call upon You, it's not in vain

Everything changes



Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, holding me still

Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, holding me still

Holding me still



You're the King of Glory

Still You hold me together

And You will be forever

My Prince of Peace

You're the King of Glory

Still You hold me together

And You will be forever

My Prince of Peace

Forever, forever



Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, holding me still

Jesus, You're still the name

Holding me still, You're holding me still

You're holding me still

Holding me still

You're holding me still
